and grade 2 tumors had a 5-year survival rate of 66.5 and 52.8%, respectively; 
grade 3 had a 3-year survival rate of 46.5%. Nodal involvement at the time of 
diagnosis had a prediction value for the 3- and 5-year survival rate of 39.8 and 
